settings.description: Now it will take me a long time to create levels.

Travel through the full and scenic views of the plains!
There's many secrets hidden!
A nuclear reactor powering Smaghettis servers. Its being shut down for bogus reasons such as, hazardous wastes, and, dangerous for the earth. No Co2, just waste that can be buried really deep.
Sometimes you have to wonder... where DO all these jumping and fire breathing statues come from? well... here's the answer.
Thwomps and Thwimps! this place is full to the brim with these mad rocky foes! think you can make it out of these ruins without getting crushed?
You and your crew are on vacation when a anomaly strikes your ship and you and your crew evacuates! You find your ship safe but 4 of your crewmates are missing! Find them! Based off: VVVVVV

Guys if you're enjoying this levels I hope you can bring me more support giving me some likes (hearts).
